  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large saucepan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and let them sizzle for 1 second.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is lightly browned, 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the prosciutto and cook for 2 minutes, until crispy.",
    "Add the lentils, water, turmeric, red chili powder, and salt. Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes, or until the lentils are tender.",
    "Stir in the cilantro and adjust the seasoning to taste.",
    "Serve hot in earthenware bowls, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
